data.characterDescription:
**Ethnicity:** African American

**Age:** Mid-to-late 20s

**Build:** Athletic, broad shoulders visible, muscular neck

**Skin:** Medium-brown complexion, smooth and even tone, slight natural sheen on forehead

**Hair:** Very short buzz cut, nearly shaved, dark black, receding slightly at temples, natural hairline with slight widow's peak

**Eyes:** Deep brown, almond-shaped, hooded lids, intense direct gaze, slight natural asymmetry with left eye appearing marginally smaller, visible lower eye bags

**Eyebrows:** Thick, naturally arched, well-defined with clean edges, dark black, slight gap/thin spot in left eyebrow near inner corner

**Face shape:** Oval to rectangular, strong angular jawline, prominent cheekbones, defined bone structure, slightly elongated face

**Nose:** Broad bridge, wide nostrils, rounded tip, medium-sized with visible small nostril piercing on left side (tiny silver stud)

**Lips:** Full, well-defined cupid's bow on upper lip, lower lip fuller than upper, natural medium-pink undertone

**Facial hair:** Thin mustache connecting to a small goatee/soul patch beneath lower lip, sparse stubble along jawline and chin, neatly trimmed

**Distinguishing marks:** Small nose piercing (left nostril), subtle beauty mark/mole visible, ears slightly protruding, pronounced Adam's apple, clean symmetrical features overall, slight five o'clock shadow on lower face

**Expression:** Neutral to subtly confident, relaxed mouth, direct eye contact, composed demeanor

**Ethnicity:** Caucasian
**Age:** late 20s
**Build:** petite, hourglass figure, slightly curvy, defined waist
**Skin:** fair, smooth, glowing
**Hair:** shoulder-length, wavy auburn, voluminous, darker roots
**Eyes:** large, almond-shaped, deep hazel, double-lid, slightly upturned outer corners
**Eyebrows:** full, natural arch, dark brown
**Face shape:** oval, soft contours, high cheekbones, small rounded chin
**Nose:** straight, refined, slightly rounded tip
**Lips:** full, defined cupid's bow, lower lip slightly fuller
**Distinguishing marks:** none visible
**Body:** wearing an off-the-shoulder lace gown with floral patterns, visible cleavage, and a delicate necklace with a pendant.
